snippet.textDisplay:
Amazing song!! Thank you for lifting our spirit.. 
But I've gotta say what needs saying: Coke Studio India spoils the entire plot trying to overdo so many things. They unnecessarily enforce fusion into classical songs, just to seem cool and relevant to the elite audience. I really felt so disappointed listening to that entire "Haiyya Haiyya" part. Totally uncalled for, totally a big spoiler. You can never make a song that is flawless. Ye kuch na kuch murakhta karte hi hain.
